# help/en/overview.ftl — Midnight Blue Theme help texts (English)

help-midnight-blue-title = Midnight Blue Theme

help-midnight-blue-body =
    Midnight Blue is the default FreeSynergy desktop theme, designed by KalEl.
    It uses deep navy and dark blue backgrounds with a vivid cyan accent that matches
    the FreeSynergy brand color. Panels have a subtle glass effect with soft shadows.

    Color palette:
    - Background: deep navy (#0f172a) and dark blue (#1e293b)
    - Accent: vivid cyan (#00bcd4) — the FreeSynergy brand color
    - Text: crisp white (#f1f5f9) and light slate for secondary text
    - Status: green for success, amber for warnings, red for errors

    The theme is designed for long work sessions in dimly lit or dark environments.
    High contrast between background and text reduces eye strain without being harsh.

help-midnight-blue-apply-title = Applying the Theme

help-midnight-blue-apply-body =
    Midnight Blue is active by default. If you switched to another theme and want
    to return to Midnight Blue:

    1. Open Desktop Settings > Appearance > Theme.
    2. Select "Midnight Blue" from the theme list.
    3. Click Apply. The change takes effect immediately — no logout required.

    All FreeSynergy programs (Desktop, Browser, Store, and installed apps) update
    their appearance instantly when the theme changes.
